  title: Towns & Places
  body: 'This place offers services for <sprite="gem" index=0> Influence: heal <sprite="Heal" index=0> wounds, buy <sprite="crystal" index=0> crystals, recruit <sprite="army" index=0> units. Assault its guardians to conquer it for a permanent reward — conquering 2 <sprite="castle" index=0> Castles wins the run.'
